"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/869451","Department for Transport","false","2018-03-27","<p>The central Department and its four executive agencies – Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency, Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency, Maritime and Coastguard Agency and Vehicle Certification Agency - have no record of entering into any contracts with SCL Group or Cambridge Analytica since 2010.</p>","Wealden","Ms Nusrat Ghani","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/869451/answer",,,,,,"2018-03-27T15:36:15.053Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/869451/answer","Biography information for Ms Nusrat Ghani","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/869451/answer",,,,,"27","Transport","Transport","2018-03-22","Department for Transport: Cambridge Analytica​ and SCL Group","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Transport, whether (a)  his Department and (b) agencies of his Department have had contracts with (a) SCL Group, (b) Cambridge Analytica.","false","Biography information for Patrick Grady","Glasgow North","Patrick Grady","133965"
